      <item>
        <title>Protective put</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Buy a &lt;a href=&quot;../instruments/put.html&quot;&gt;put&lt;/a&gt; option to protect
a portfolio from downside risk. You lose at most the premium paid for the put
option, but you participate if the underlying is gaining in value.&lt;/p&gt;

